    "description": "<p>A warrior well-versed with the arts of protection. Not just for themselves but their allies as well. Despite their strength, they're vulnerable particularly to fire.</p>",
    "attacks": "<p><strong>Inflict Violence: Sword and Shield.</strong> Attack an adjacent fighter with Bravery, and then taunt them until the end of the Guard's next riff.</p><p><strong>Gambits</strong> [[/r d4]]</p><p><strong>1:</strong> Rush &gt; Rush to a better position to guard allies &gt; Inflict Violence</p><p><strong>2:</strong> Rush &gt; <strong>Mass Threat [2]:</strong> Roll 1 attack die against all enemies in burst 3, and then taunt them until the end of the Guard's next riff.</p><p><strong>3:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; <strong>Shield Bash [1]:</strong> Attack an adjacent fighter with Bravery, and then 50% chance of <strong>stunning</strong> them.</p><p><strong>4:</strong> <strong>Shield Charge [1]:</strong> Rush double your Speed, moving through enemies. Any enemies moved through are <strong>slowed</strong> &gt; <strong>Shield Bash [1]</strong> &gt; Inflict Violence</p>",
